<p>For code syntax coloration I’m using Darcula theme from Intellij IDEA, which I’ve found in this post <a href="http://smasue.github.io/pygments-darcula">Darcula theme for Pygments</a>.</p>

<p>XML with line numbers (linenos flag), <code class="highlighter-rouge">{% highlight xml linenos %}</code>:</p>

