<span class="o">}</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>To add name to the code snippet, as in the examples above, add following construction before the snippet:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="o">&gt;</span>Java
<span class="o">{</span>:.filename<span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">{</span>% highlight java %<span class="o">}</span>
...</code></pre></figure>

